{"tid":1807190,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[1月新番] Re:Zero 從零開始的異世界生活 新編集版","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T08:12:39.000Z","uid":12110,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"188756dacb279239fadf35149bd205b2402ce5fe","tid":1807190,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/49/38c73bc723179c0188c51ee64917dgh5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F49%2F38c73bc723179c0188c51ee64917dgh5.JPG&h=c74ee9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n普通的高中生 菜月昴從便利商店回家的路上，突然被召喚到異世界，遭遇強盜面臨性命危機，這時遇到了一位銀髮少女拯救了他，以報恩為名義，昴自告奮勇要幫助少女找東西。好不容易才掌握到線索，昴和少女卻被不明人士攻擊而死亡，但回過神來，昴卻發現自己置身在第一次被召喚到異世界時的所在位置，這是昴得到的能力──「死亡 回歸」，死後時間會倒轉回到一開始。昴必須要跨越無數絕望，從死亡的命運中拯救少女！<br />\n<br />\n  本次新編版將第一季動畫追加新場景，彙整成一小時特別篇，將於 2020 年 1 月 1 日播出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bwq7HxrHiZU&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBwq7HxrHiZU%26feature%3Demb_title&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=2360e16e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bwq7HxrHiZU&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZSeOwctpIg0&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZSeOwctpIg0%26feature%3Demb_title&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=7c0308bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZSeOwctpIg0&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n將第一季2集變做1集一個鐘咁播，應該會另加少少新野+細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為4月第2季鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f69eb953ed8325c120f80bcb811b04388633b0c","tid":1807190,"uid":127705,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"ci